data.description: Don't miss this assumable existing 2.25% VA loan! Do NOT have to be a VA qualified buyer. VRBO okay! Glorious glorious sunrises  greet you , and fabulous views of Mt Baker and the Cascade Mtns. Over 2000 sq. ft. of rambler {no stairs} for easy living and large deck across the back for those enjoyable Whidbey Island evenings to sit outside while you watch the sailboats go by. Beautiful wood floors and open beams greet you as you walk in the main entry and immediately your eyes are drawn to waterside wall of windows and the fantastic views . Den could be used as an extra bedroom. Fully fenced large yard for pet safety . Neighbors lot has a tree at edge of bluff the eagles  love to sit in as they watch for prey. Owner agent.
